ard\n| John Hurt\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"|[[Golden Trailer Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"|31 May 2012\n| Best Drama Trailer\n|\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Thriller Trailer\n|\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Independent Poster\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Drama Poster\n|\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\"|Georgia Film Critics Association\n| rowspan=\"8\"| 16 January 2012\n| Best Film\n|\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Director\n| Tomas Alfredson\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Actor in a Leading Role\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Supporting Actor\n| Tom Hardy\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Ensemble Cast\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Adapted Screenplay\n| Bridget O'Connor, Peter Straughan\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Cinematography\n| Hoyte van Hoytema\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Production Design\n| Maria Djurkovic\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Gotham Awards|Gotham Independent Film Awards]]\n| [[Gotham Independent Film Awards 2011|18 November 2011]]\n| [[Gotham Independent Film Awards 2011|Gotham Tribute Award]]\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Hollywood Film Festival]]\n| 24 October 2011\n| [[Hollywood Film Festival|Best Composer]]\n| Alberto Iglesias\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"|International Chinephile Society\n| rowspan=\"4\"|22 February 2012\n| Best Cast\n|\n| {{draw|Runner-up}}\n|-\n| Best Adapted Screenplay\n| Bridget O'Connor, Peter Straughan\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Production Design\n| Maria Djurkovic\n| {{draw|Runner-up}}\n|-\n| Best Original Score\n| Alberto Iglesias\n| {{draw|Runner-up}}\n|-\n||[[International Federation of Film Critics|International Federation of Film Critics Award]]\n||10 September 2012\n| [[International Federation of Film Critics|Grand Prix for the best film]]\n| Tomas Alfredson\n| {{draw|9th Place}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"10\"|[[International Online Film Critics' Poll]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flickeringmyth.com/2012/12/international-online-film-critics-poll.html|title=International Online Film Critics Poll unveil nominees|publisher=Flickering Myth|date=1 December 2012|accessdate=18 August 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flickeringmyth.com/2012/12/international-online-film-critics-poll_20.html|title=International Online Film Critics Poll declares 3rd edition winners|publisher=Flickering Myth|date=20 December 2012|accessdate=18 August 2013}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"10\"|20 December 2012\n| Best Film \u2013 Motion Picture\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Top Ten Films\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Director\n| Tomas Alfredson\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Actor in a Leading Role\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Ensemble Cast\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Adapted Screenplay\n| Bridget O'Connor, Peter Straughan\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Cinematography\n| Hoyte van Hoytema\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Production Design\n| Maria Djurkovic\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Editing\n| Dino Jons\u00e4ter\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Original Score\n| Alberto Iglesias\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|[[Irish Film and Television Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"3\"|11 February 2012\n| Best International Film\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Actor in a Lead Role in a Feature Film\n| Ciar\u00e1n Hinds\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| International Actor\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\"|Italian Online Film Actors & Dubbers Award\n| rowspan=\"5\"| 1 September 2012\n| Best Foreign Actor\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Foreign Supporting Actor\n| Tom Hardy\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Foreign Cast\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Male Dubber\n| Stefano De Sando\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Public Choice Award for Best Performance\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" | Italy Screenplay Prize\n| rowspan=\"5\" | 13 July 2012\n| Best Film\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Top Ten Films\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Adapted Screenplay \u2013 International\n| Bridget O'Connor, Peter Straughan\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Special Award for Best Director\n| Tomas Alfredson\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Special Award for Best Performance\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\"|Las Vegas Film Critics Society\n| rowspan=\"5\"| 13 December 2011\n| Best Actor\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{nom}}\n