est Actor\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Adapted Screenplay\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Production Design\n| Maria Djurkovic\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Cast\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Casting\n| Jina Jay\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Palm Springs International Film Festival]]\n| 15 January 2012\n| [[Palm Springs International Film Festival|Best International Star]]\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Phoenix Film Critics Society\n| 27 December 2011\n| Best Actor\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\"|Premio Cinema Ludus<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cinemaitaliano.info/news/15606/i-vincitori-del-premio-cinema-ludus-2012.html|title=I vincitori del Premio Cinema Ludus 2012|work=cinemaitaliano.info}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"8\"|19 November 2012\n| Gran Prix for Best Film\n| Tomas Alfredson\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Prix for Best Actor\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best European Film\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best European Director\n| Tomas Alfredson\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best European Actor\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best European Screenplay\n| Bridget O'Connor, Peter Straughan\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best European Technical Achievement\n| Maria Djurkovic\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Producer\n| Tim Bevan, Eric Fellner\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"|[[Richard Attenborough|Richard Attenborough Regional Film Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2 February 2012\n| Best British Film of the year\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Actor of the year\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best British Actor of the year\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Screenplay\n| Bridget O'Connor, Peter Straughan\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[San Francisco Film Critics Circle]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"|25 March 2012\n| [[San Francisco Film Critics Circle Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n| Gary Oldman\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[San Francisco Film Critics Circle Award for Best Adapted Screenplay|Best Adapted Screenplay]]\n| Bridget O'Connor, Peter Straughan\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|[[Satellite Award]]\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 18 December 2011\n| [[Sa